                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Measuring the activity of",
                "these products and using the recommended cross",
                "section values of IAEA  it is possible to calculate",
                "the current of the beam and then using it to determine",
                "the thick target yields of 211At and 210At."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE",
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A HPGe gamma spectrometer was utilized to",
                "detect 211At, 211Po and  210At, while a Si (ion",
                "implanted) alpha detector was used for the detection",
                "of 211At,  211Po and 210Po."
              ]
            }
          ],
